---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import teamImage from "@images/team.webp";
---

<div class="space-y-16 md:space-y-20">
  <!-- Headline -->
  <div class="max-w-lg border-b pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">
      Discover the essence of our company
    </h2>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">Mission</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
        We deliver high-quality cannabis products by combining data-driven
        decision-making with rigorous processes that ensure consistency and
        excellence. Through innovation and precision, we provide our customers
        with reliable, top-tier products that meet the highest industry
        standards.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision Section -->
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">Vision</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
        To be the most trusted provider of premium cannabis in the European
        market, setting new benchmarks for quality, transparency, and innovation
        while ensuring every product meets strict regulatory and safety
        standards.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">Values</h3>

      <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-2">
            CUSTOMER FOCUSED
          </h4>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            We prioritize our clients' needs, delivering reliable, high-quality
            products that exceed expectations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-2">DATA DRIVEN</h4>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            We believe in what the numbers tell us, using data to optimize every
            step of our process.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-2">
            PROCESS ORIENTED
          </h4>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Consistency and quality are at the core of what we do, supported by
            structured workflows and precision.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Team Image -->
  <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-md overflow-hidden">
      <Image
        src={teamImage}
        alt="Groqo team in clean room attire"
        class="w-full h-auto"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
